{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"vwa.la help","description":"Everything you need to know about the vwa.la influencer marketing platform."}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Influencer/group specific commission","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"How to reward influencers differently?","meta_description":"","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"merchant","toc":null,"keywords":["merchant","help"]},"html":"<p>You can reward influencers differently by segmenting your influencers into groups. You can then set group specific commission rules in your promotion policy.</p>\n<h2 id=\"instructions\"><a href=\"#instructions\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Instructions</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Go to the influencer page</li>\n<li>Select the influencer group tab and create a new group (you can re-name groups by clicking on the name column).</li>\n<li>To assign 1 or more influencers to a group, go back to the influencer tab. In the influencer table, select 1 or more influencers and in the action menu, click 'change group'. You can then choose the new group for the selected influencers.</li>\n<li>Once you have finished creating groups, you must go to the promotion policy menu and configure the group's commission rules.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"create--re-name-influencer-groups\"><a href=\"#create--re-name-influencer-groups\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Create / re-name influencer groups</h4>\n<p><img src=\"/images/merchant/_create_ag.png\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"assign-1-or-more-influencers-to-a-group\"><a href=\"#assign-1-or-more-influencers-to-a-group\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Assign 1 or more influencers to a group</h4>\n<p><img src=\"/images/merchant/_change_ag.png\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"then-go-to-the-promotion-policy-page-and-configure-commission-rules\"><a href=\"#then-go-to-the-promotion-policy-page-and-configure-commission-rules\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Then go to the promotion policy page and configure commission rules</h4>\n<p><img src=\"/images/merchant/2017-10-11-23-34-06.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"what-group-names-should-i-choose\"><a href=\"#what-group-names-should-i-choose\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>What group names should I choose?</h2>\n<p>It is common to use influencer groups to create tiered commission structures for your influencers. Here are some common naming conventions that you can use:</p>\n<p><strong>Suggested pattern 1</strong>\nBronze (rename the default group)<br>\nSilver<br>\nGold</p>\n<p><strong>Suggested pattern 2</strong>\nNewbie (rename the default group)<br>\nStandard<br>\nVIP</p>\n<p><strong>Suggested pattern 3</strong>\nTier 1 (rename the default group)<br>\nTier 2<br>\nTier 3</p>\n<p>These are just suggestions. You can get as creative as you like :)</p>\n<h2 id=\"is-there-a-best-practise-for-naming-groups\"><a href=\"#is-there-a-best-practise-for-naming-groups\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Is there a best practise for naming groups?</h2>\n<p>We recommend that you do not add promotion details (i.e. 15% off) to your group names. This is because it is likely that a group's commission policy will change over time. For this reason, we prohibit symbols from being included in group names.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/merchant/influencer-group-specific-commission/"},"timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"You can reward influencers differently by segmenting your influencers into groups. You can then set group specific commission rules in yourâ€¦"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/merchant/influencer-group-specific-commission/"}}